[SN]TITLE[SN]
BMW reveals helmet-free motorcycle concept

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Motoring giant BMW has unveiled a self-balancing concept motorcycle, which it says could represent the future of transportation.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
12 October 2016 Last updated at 18:20 BST
The company says artificial intelligence systems would make it safe enough to ride without a helmet.
